FBIS4-50893 "drchi099_h_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-099 Daily Report 13 May 1994 West Europe Song Jian Presents Award to EU Information Director Song Jian Presents Award to EU Information Director OW2105073194 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 1131 GMT 13 May 94 OW2105073194 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service Chinese BFN [By reporter Yang Zhaobo (2799 0340 3134)] [Excerpt] Beijing, 13 May (XINHUA) -- State Councillor and Minister in Charge of the State Science and Technology Commission Song Jian presented to (?Carpentier) [ka bang di er 0595 6721 5530 1422], director general of the European Union's General Office of Information, the 1993 "China's International Scientific and Technological Cooperation Award," at the Great Hall of the People today. It has been learned that Mr. (?Carpentier) was director general of the European Union's General Office of Energy Resources, and has become director general of the European Union's General Office of Information since 1986. He has won several international scientific and technological achievements awards. He was conferred an honorary title of foreign academician by the Swedish Royal College of Engineering Science in 1989. It was another extraordinary compliment for him to win the 1993 "China's International Scientific and Technological Cooperation Award." [passage omitted]
